## Roadmap — Milestones & Acceptance

Source: [docs/roadmap.md](mdc:docs/roadmap.md)

Standards:
- Concurrency: 3 one-shot max (FIFO); Timeouts: 120s send; 5s tmux.
- Logging NDJSON par agent: `./logs/{project}/{role}.ndjson`.
- Exit codes: 0,1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8 (voir CLI reference).

Milestones M0–M9 (extraits):
- M0 Doctor/Config — `doctor`, `config validate`
- M1 Data Model — `db init`, `project add`, `agent add`
- M2 Providers One-shot — `session start`, `send`
- M3 Session Resume — `session list`, `session resume`
- M4 tmux Agents — `agent run|attach|stop`
- M5 Broadcast — `broadcast --mode oneshot|repl`
- M6 TUI — `tui`
- M7 Routing — `send --to @role|@all`
- M8 Git Context — `context git --status|--diff|--log`
- M9 Robustness/Observability — `send --timeout`, `broadcast --verbose`
